<title>USA: ServiceMaster buys WMX's 19 pct holding.</title>
<headline>ServiceMaster buys WMX's 19 pct holding.</headline>
<dateline>DOWNERS GROVE, Ill. 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>ServiceMaster LP said Tuesday it completed the purchase of WMX Technologies Inc's 19 percent ownership interest in ServiceMaster.</p>
<p>As announced in February, the two companies agreed that ServiceMaster would buy WMX's entire ownership interest in ServiceMaster for about $626 million in cash.</p>
<p>WMX owned 27.2 million restricted shares of ServiceMaster and also had an option to buy an additional 1.9 million shares that was cancelled as part of the transaction.</p>
